I have some concerns about the monthly charges. They seem higher than expected.

Sure, it's four five six seven.

Perfect. Can you also confirm the email address associated with your account?

It's carolyn.rodriguez@email.com.

Maybe. I’d like to think about it and discuss with my spouse first.

Of course, Carolyn. Take your time and feel free to reach out if you have any more questions. Thank you for your time today and have a great day!
